    "spell_type": "spell",
    "subtype": "spell",
    "text": "You conjure a poisonous fog. This functions as *mist*, except the area moves 10 feet away from you each round. A breathing creature that starts its turn in the area takes 6d8 poison damage with a basic Fortitude save. You can Dismiss the spell.",
